    "Another limitation is the diversity of LLMs used was low.",
    "Most articles in our review focused on variants of BERT and ChatGPT.",
    "Therefore, this review provides only a limited picture of the variability we might expect in applicability between different LLMs.",
    "Another limitation is the rapid evolution of LLMs.",
    "For example, studies using GPT-3.5-turbo do not incorporate advancements in subsequent models"
